Fucking awesome.

Weird how in a site dedicated to imaging how reality can be distorted, and how human beings respond to those distortions, we each have our own line between lame strangeness (-) and fantastic strangeness (+). The more I read on here I become progressively more uncertain where exactly that line is and why it's there in the first place, but whatever this SCP is doing, it's doing it right.







